Package cams.util.exception

package cams.util.exception
  • Exception Classes
    Class
    Description
    AlreadyProcessedException
    Custom exception that is thrown when a requested model cannot be found in a repository.
    MenuChoiceInvalidException
    Custom exception for invalid menu choices.
    ModelAlreadyExistsException
    Custom exception that is thrown when an attempt is made to add a model to a repository that already contains a model with the same ID.
    ModelNotFoundException
    Custom exception that is thrown when a requested model cannot be found in a repository.
    OperationCancelledException
    Custom exception that is thrown when a delete operation is cancelled.
    ParticipantAlreadyRegisteredException
    Custom exception that is thrown when user attempts to delete a camp or make a camp invisible when the camp already has participants.
    PasswordIncorrectException
    The PasswordIncorrectException class represents an exception that is thrown when a password entered by the user is incorrect.
